# Referral of Unresolved Customer Grievance

1. Thank you for bringing your concern to our attention. We understand the importance of resolving your issue promptly.

2. As your grievance requires further investigation, we are referring your case to the designated department best equipped to assist you.

3. A specialized team member will review your case and contact you with an update or resolution as soon as possible.

4. If you have any additional information or documentation, please provide it to help expedite the process.

5. We appreciate your patience and will ensure your concern is addressed thoroughly.
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
